data.description: Fantastic 4 bedroom home 5 mins from Gate 8!! NO HOA! You will not want to miss this single story, split floor plan home. When you walk in you'll find a designated foyer leading into the living room with vaulted ceiling. Open floor plan connects the dining area and beautiful kitchen. Kitchen has espresso cabinets, peninsula with room for bar stools, and stainless appliances. Walk in pantry/laundry as well. Spacious primary suite features tray ceiling, large walk-in closet, and bathroom with double sinks, walk-in shower, and separate tub. 3 more bedrooms and full bath on the opposite side of the home. Don't forget about the 2 car garage and private fenced in backyard with open patio!
